{"about_the_game":"<u><strong>Become a Card-Slinging Witch</strong></u><br>Spellcard Academy is a roguelike deckbuilder where you play as a witch studying wacky schools of magic like Llamamancy and Spookymancy. Summon monsters to fight for you. Scrounge together components to cast powerful spells. Mix and match spell combos as you journey for lost astral knowledge.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/demon_fight_compressed_2.gif?t=1736777600\" /><br><br><u><strong>TCG-Style Combat</strong></u><br>Summon your own monsters to protect yourself, putting tough ones in the front row and ranged ones in the back! Carefully manage your spell components and energy each turn. Pop off and vanquish monsters and bosses with your powerful spell combos!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/ravencaller_fight_compressed_2.gif?t=1736777600\" /><br><br><u><strong>Unique Schools of Magic</strong></u><br>Summon powerful familiars to do your bidding, sacrifice llamas to spawn even more llamas, and transmute resources to summon massive golems. Mix and match spells from different schools of magic to discover new strategies! Find or buy magical trinkets to make your build even more unique!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/combos_compressed_2.gif?t=1736777600\" /><br><br><u><strong>Explore Procedural Dungeons</strong></u><br>Get into trouble! Talk to strangers! Buy a new pair of magic socks!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1037250/extras/explore_compressed_2.gif?t=1736777600\" /><br><br><u><strong>Meta Progression</strong></u><br>Level up and permanently unlock new cards that might appear in future journeys on Academy Island!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store